					<span class="meta-date"><a href="https://advising.uic.edu/share-with-students-become-a-peer-success-coach/" title="SHARE WITH STUDENTS: Become a Peer Success Coach!" rel="bookmark">
						<span class="month">Apr</span>
						<span class="day">20</span>
						<span class="year">2018</span>
					</a></span>


					

					<span class="meta-author"><span>by jvolpe</span></span>

				</div>
                
				<div class="post-contents">
										<h3 class="entry-title">
					<a href="https://advising.uic.edu/share-with-students-become-a-peer-success-coach/" title="SHARE WITH STUDENTS: Become a Peer Success Coach!" rel="bookmark">SHARE WITH STUDENTS: Become a Peer Success Coach!</a>
					</h3>
                    					    <div class="post-category">Posted in <a href="https://advising.uic.edu/category/advising-weekly-updates/">Advising Weekly Updates</a>, <a href="https://advising.uic.edu/category/share-with-students/">Share with Students</a></div>
                    					<div class="post-content">
					<p>We believe the right person, at the right time, can change a life. Success peer coaches help other students adjust to college life, realize true potential, and assist in accomplishing dreams. A Peer Coach empowers students to thrive both inside and outside of the classroom. We want you to be a part of our team!</p>
<p>STUDENT LEADERSHIP POSITION<br />
$12 per hour<br />
Up to 15 hours per week<br />
Flexible hours/schedule<br />
Help fellow students</p>
<p><em>QUALIFICATIONS </em></p>
<ul>
<li>Experience or involvement in a leadership role at UIC and/or in the community</li>
<li>Demonstrated experience working with diverse groups</li>
<li>Demonstrated effective verbal and written communication skills</li>
<li>Strong customer service, problem-solving, and relation management skills</li>
<li>Must be able to attend in-person training August 20–24</li>
<li>Must be at least a second-year student in good academic standing</li>
<li>Minimum G.P.A. requirement of 3.0</li>
</ul>
<p><em>TO APPLY</em><br />
Please submit the following documents, in addition to your completed application to: <a href="https://forms.uofi.uic.edu/sec/4358795">https://forms.uofi.uic.edu/sec/4358795</a><br />
Unofficial transcript(s)<br />
One-page resume<br />
Cover letter<br />
Letter of recommendation from former/current supervisor or faculty</p>
<p><em>FOR QUESTIONS AND INQUIRIES</em><br />
Contact: <a href="mailto:aceinfo@uic.edu">aceinfo@uic.edu</a></p>
<p><a href="https://uofi.box.com/s/li3bvodt0cd5lpg6mfcf8pn8vfatbdun">Dowload the flyer to post for students!</a></p>
					</div>
