<a href="http://csrc.uic.edu/events/connect-with-the-campus-advocacy-network-can/">http://csrc.uic.edu/events/connect-with-the-campus-advocacy-network-can/</a></p>
<p><strong>Commuter Living Room (Flyer Attached)</strong><br />
Wed. April 25, 2018<br />
2:00PM-5:30PM – Commuter Student Resource Center Main Lounge<br />
<a href="http://csrc.uic.edu/events/commuter-living-room/">http://csrc.uic.edu/events/commuter-living-room/</a></p>
<p><strong>Commuter Meet-Up: Kinjaz (Flyer Attached)</strong><br />
Wed. April 25, 2018<br />
5:30PM – Commuter Student Resource Center Main Lounge<br />
<a href="http://csrc.uic.edu/events/commuter-meet-up-kinjaz/">http://csrc.uic.edu/events/commuter-meet-up-kinjaz/</a></p>
